## 📦 포함된 기능

### Core (5,764 LOC)
- ✅ Lexer (토크나이저)
- ✅ Parser (RD + Pratt 파싱)
- ✅ Type Checker (정적 타입)
- ✅ Bytecode Compiler
- ✅ Stack VM (실행)
- ✅ Move Semantics

### Standard Library (59개 함수)
- ✅ String (14) - split, join, contains, uppercase, lowercase, etc
- ✅ Functional (9) - map, filter, reduce, fold, any, all, etc
- ✅ Regex (7) - match, test, replace, exec, etc
- ✅ JSON (6) - parse, stringify, pretty, encode, decode, etc
- ✅ Database (9) - query, insert, update, delete, etc

### Runtime Extensions
- ✅ HTTP (5 functions) - Zero-copy pipeline, Reactor pattern
- ✅ JIT (5-stage) - Hotspot detection, IC, PGO, Codegen, Deopt
- ✅ Actor Model - Message-based concurrency
- ✅ Database (ORM + SQLite) - Transaction, Query optimization

### Security
- ✅ Crypto - AES, RSA, HMAC
- ✅ Validation - SQLi, XSS prevention, type checking
- ✅ Audit - Decision tracking, compliance logging
- ✅ Compliance - GDPR, SOC2, ISO27001

### Developer Tools
- ✅ IDE Plugin - Stack VM visualization, Actor monitoring
- ✅ Migration - v3 → v4 upgrade path
- ✅ Testing - 400+ test cases (100% pass rate)

